headline: New Data Monitoring Service Option Now Available for Cessna Citation and Cessna SkyCourier Customers
summary: WICHITA, Kan., June 02, 2025--Textron Aviation announced customers can now choose to transfer their flight data through GE Aerospace’s C-FOQA service.
